Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}第二話 吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀 我說菊千代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次是頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真討厭呢 又要拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是銳利的切口呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來不像是簡單的打架吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是打架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊千代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方是武士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是武士 就是武士呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 水巫女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個武士大人比我想象中要跑的還快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道走哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是犯愁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是農民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很少見呢
